OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778868675
OL,3,CFire station cuts will 'cost lives'
OL,4,Csay protesters gathered at county hall
OL,6,FProposals to close eight fire stations
OL,7,Fin Dorset and Wiltshire will "cost
OL,8,Flives", opponents say.
OL,10,FProtesters gathered outside Dorset
OL,11,FCounty Hall today, Thursday 14 May, to
OL,12,Fask the fire authority to reconsider
OL,13,Fthe cuts.
OL,15,FDorset and Wiltshire Fire and Rescue
OL,16,FService has proposed the closures to
OL,17,Fsave money, as it faces a decline in
OL,18,Fgovernment grants and a funding
OL,19,Fshortfall of #1.2million in 2026-27.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
