FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778868675
OL,3,CFire station cuts will 'cost lives'
OL,4,Csay protesters gathered at county hall
OL,6,FA public consultation into the cuts
OL,7,Fopened in February and closes
OL,8,Ftomorrow, Friday 15 May.
OL,10,FOpponents from the Save Our Fire
OL,11,FStations campaign say they want to
OL,12,Fknow how the closures will impact the
OL,13,Fcounties' emergency and disaster plans.
OL,15,FCampaigner Carol King, who opposes the
OL,16,Fclosures, said: "We're fearful that
OL,17,Four lives ` and those of our children
OL,18,Fand grandchildren - will be put in
OL,19,Fdanger by these fire station cuts.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778868675
OL,3,CFire station cuts will 'cost lives'
OL,4,Csay protesters gathered at county hall
OL,6,F"Fire Authority bosses openly admits
OL,7,Fthat their plans will cost lives."
OL,9,F"Rural villages, like those in my own
OL,10,Fhometown of Maiden Newton, are
OL,11,Fvulnerable to thatched roof fires and
OL,12,Fthe increasing danger of grassland and
OL,13,Fheath blazes.
OL,15,F"The crazy thing is that climate
OL,16,Fchange is increasing the risk of fires
OL,17,Fgrowing out of control ` And they want
OL,18,Fto cut down on fire stations and the
OL,19,Ffirefighters on call to save us."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778868675
OL,3,CFire station cuts will 'cost lives'
OL,4,Csay protesters gathered at county hall
OL,6,FAnother opponent to the plans, Pam
OL,7,FStrange, said: "When your house is on
OL,8,Ffire, you truly realise that minutes
OL,9,Fmatter.
OL,11,F"If our fire station closes, then
OL,12,Fresponse times will rise. I don't want
OL,13,Fto be trapped with my grandchildren in
OL,14,Fa burning building when firefighters
OL,15,Fhave to drive the eight or more miles
OL,16,Ffrom Dorchester before they even begin
OL,17,Ftackling the fire."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
