PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778868675
OL,3,CFire station cuts will 'cost lives'
OL,4,Csay protesters gathered at county hall
OL,6,FProtestors met last week with local MP
OL,7,FEdward Morello at Maiden Newton fire
OL,8,Fstation, which is one of the locations
OL,9,Fat risk of closure.
OL,11,FThey say firefighters from Maiden
OL,12,FNewton have "saved historic properties
OL,13,Ffrom burning down in the village in
OL,14,Frecent years" and "saved lives in
OL,15,Ftraffic accidents on the nearby, busy
OL,16,FA37".
OL,18,FCampaigners say volunteer on-call
OL,19,Ffirefighters reached the scene within
OL,20,Fminutes when a fire threatened to
OL,21,Fdestroy the historic parish church.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778868675
OL,3,CFire station cuts will 'cost lives'
OL,4,Csay protesters gathered at county hall
OL,6,FVicar, the Rev Tim Greenslade, said:
OL,7,F"Our medieval church would have been
OL,8,Fmuch more damaged by the fire, had not
OL,9,Fthe fire brigade arrived so quickly."
OL,11,FA 10-year-old girl, Lila-Claire, who
OL,12,Fwas rescued with her family from a car
OL,13,Fcrash, is also supporting the campaign.
OL,15,FIn response to local opposition, chief
OL,16,Ffire officer for Dorset and Wiltshire
OL,17,FAndy Cole said the service was facing
OL,18,F"challenging financial times".
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
