OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778868675
OL,3,CFire station cuts will 'cost lives'
OL,4,Csay protesters gathered at county hall
OL,6,F"Despite making over #15m in savings
OL,7,Fsince the combination of Dorset and
OL,8,FWiltshire Fire and Rescue Services, we
OL,9,Fare now facing a 19.5% reduction in
OL,10,Fgovernment funding over the settlement
OL,11,Fperiod.
OL,13,F"This results in a budget deficit of
OL,14,F#1.2m in 2026/27, growing to #1.7m in
OL,15,F2028/29. We know that proposing fire
OL,16,Fstation closures is not welcome for
OL,17,Four communities or our staff.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778868675
OL,3,CFire station cuts will 'cost lives'
OL,4,Csay protesters gathered at county hall
OL,6,F"However, the Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FAuthority are out to public
OL,8,Fconsultation on proposals to close
OL,9,Feight fire stations.
OL,11,F"I continue to work with all our local
OL,12,FMPs to lobby for better funding for
OL,13,Ffire & rescue services. The public
OL,14,Fconsultation is open until Friday 15th
OL,15,FMay so it would not be appropriate for
OL,16,Fus to comment further at this time.
OL,18,F"I would urge all local residents to
OL,19,Fparticipate in the consultation, which
OL,20,Fthey can do via our website."
OL,26,@|D@]O]
